    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing. This example delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is secured with a documented rear subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its signature handling characteristics via a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains mechanically synchronized and robust. A purist\u2019s machine with the rod bearing service already performed.",
