      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is super reliable and totally ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
